                                    <p>1.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>Each participant of the NDC Course is required to write a thesis </strong> . While preparing a thesis, a course member will get an opportunity to study the selected subject in detail and would thus acquire some specialisation in it.</p>
                                    <p>2.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;These notes explain the norms, specify the assignment and provide guidelines for thesis writing. The notes are laid out in two parts as follows:</p>
