                                    <hr />
                                    <h3 class="text-primary"><strong>Aim</strong></h3>
                                    <p>3.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The aim of the individual thesis is to enable Course Members to research and study a chosen subject of national or international interest and to make an <strong>original contribution</strong> to the existing knowledge on the subject.</p>
                                    <hr />
                                    <h3 class="text-primary"><strong>Selection of a Topic</strong></h3>
                                    <p>4.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;While selecting a topic the following points may be kept in view:‑</p>
