                                    <p>&sup1;Eugene A. Forsey, &ldquo;Was the Governor General&rsquo;s Refusal Constitutional?&rdquo;, cited in Paul Fox, Politics: Canada (Toronto: Mcgraw-Hill Company of Canada Ltd., 1966), 186.</p>
                                    <hr />
