                                    <p>The abbreviation to be used is &ldquo;Ibid.,&rdquo; a Latin word meaning &ldquo;in the same.&rdquo; (Notice that Ibid. Is not underlined). Ibid. Can be used by itself, if you are referring to the same page as the previous footnote does, or it can be combined with a page number or numbers.</p>
